{"tid":973010,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知點解你女朋友同你一齊好耐都唔比你扑？","createTime":"2019-01-07T21:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T00:38:10.000Z","uid":57076,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"41ee2c60a45cd42e2f19c968cb816a00c46ab067","tid":973010,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T21:08:02.000Z","msg":"睇圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/037HoXr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F037HoXr.png&h=326f74cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\n女人一定會講：未認定對方係男朋友係老公所以唔比佢屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n潛台詞？ 係窮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你有錢？ 女人會唔想嫁入豪門？<br />\n係女都會主動想上你屋企，日日騎你，起身主動幫你含啦。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">利申：窮柒毒</span></span>"},{"pid":"8de66247817a8184217463dc3d66105315693b6e","tid":973010,"uid":195009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T21:09:08.000Z","msg":"你又知龍仔冇扑？"},{"pid":"815abca1bc697ef0bb7d7daf8a0cabc7c6f9f42b","tid":973010,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8de66247817a8184217463dc3d66105315693b6e","tid":973010,"uid":195009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T21:09:08.000Z","msg":"你又知龍仔冇扑？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T21:13:15.000Z","msg":"因為王君馨(Grace)喺一次訪問，自爆仲係處女，令佢一夜成名， 冇耐呢個處女宣言一出，其他圈中教友包括鍾嘉欣、李亞男、苟芸慧同岑麗香，亦相繼宣示處子身，於是有「處女黨」稱號。（蘋果日報）<br />\n<br />\n由於鍾嘉欣是基督徒，又被認為是處女，卻有婚前懷孕之嫌，網民此時都不乏冷嘲熱諷的留言：「處女 產子皆神蹟」。（網典）"},{"pid":"54c7ad87489b7fc0b37a7e9dc2dfaac6cc77a3c1","tid":973010,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T00:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}